  new upstream version, fixes #90838. also did some cleanup.

  18 Dec 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> wavpack-4.1.ebuild:
  Stable amd64, sparc, x86.

  28 Sep 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> wavpack-4.0.ebuild,
  wavpack-4.1.ebuild:
  Removed autoconf from RDEPEND.  Added to ~sparc and ~amd64.

  23 Sep 2004; Patrick Dawson <pkdawson@gentoo.org> +wavpack-4.1.ebuild:
  version bump

  03 Sep 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> wavpack-4.0.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

*wavpack-4.0 (20 Aug 2004)

